tournament.name: Redbull Battle Grounds SFV Churning the Butter 87
tournament.details:
Come out to a #RedBullBattleGrounds edition of Game Night. ShowDown will be hosting a special Churning The Butter SFV tournament with the winner and RANDOMLY chosen entrant both receiving Hotel, Airfare, and Tickets to attend the Red Bull Battle Grounds in Seattle November 4-6, 2016!

- WHAT IS RED BULL BATTLE GROUNDS
Red Bull Battle Grounds is a premier, TV quality tournament format that contains Qualifiers, Playoffs, and a banger Final event. This year, in partnership with Capcom and Twitch, the Capcom Pro Tour North American Finals will be held at Red Bull Battle Grounds. Red Bull Battle Grounds is the last CPT Premier stop in North America before the Capcom Cup, making it the last chance for some to qualify. 
Event URL: www.redbullbattlegrounds.com

Use code “showdown” for $5 off RBBG tickets at https://smash.gg/…/capcom-pro-tour-north-american-finals-at…
